## Acknowledgments

This project builds upon the following published research:

- **Safety Layers** (ICLR 2025): Methodology for layer-wise safety attribute detection
- **Bang et al.** (ACL 2024): Topic-specific stance analysis and content/style decomposition
- **Zhou et al.** (EMNLP 2024): Weak classifier probing for representation analysis
- **Zou et al.**: Representation Engineering (RepE) and CAA steering techniques

Code implementations are original but derive from these open-access methodologies.
